    <h2>Join Our Team</h2>
    <p>At Daytona, we are driven by the vision of accelerating developer velocity and redefining the future of development environments. We create a streamlined, scalable, and secure workflow by eliminating operational bottlenecks and propelling innovation.</p>
    <p>If you're passionate about making a significant impact within the developer community and are eager to thrive in a dynamic and collaborative setting, we invite you to explore our open positions.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="why-work">
    <h2>Why Work with Us?</h2>
    <p>Become part of an environment where each member contributes to our collective success. We share a mission to deliver a transformative development experience. When you join Daytona, you join a journey to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Develop groundbreaking technologies that empower software professionals.</li>
      <li>Contribute to a platform that improves the daily lives of developers.</li>
      <li>Collaborate with a team of experts passionate about their crafts.</li>
      <li>Engage with an inclusive culture that values every voice.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="our-culture">
    <h2>Our Culture</h2>
    <p>Daytona's culture revolves around our core values:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Empathy and Respect:</strong> Understanding and valuing the perspective of every team member.</li>
      <li><strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> Fostering a culture that encourages personal and professional growth.</li>
      <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Championing creativity and new ideas within an ever-evolving industry.</li>
      <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> Taking initiative and ownership of our work and its impact on our users.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="career-development">
    <h2>Career Development</h2>
    <p>We are committed to the development of our team:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Advancement Opportunities:</strong> At Daytona, merit leads the way in career progression.</li>
      <li><strong>Learning Resources:</strong> Access to courses, conferences, and workshops to aid your growth.</li>
      <li><strong>Mentorship:</strong> Collaborate with and learn from industry leaders.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="why-join">
    <h2>Why Join Daytona?</h2>
    <p>We're not just investing in innovation; we're investing in you. At Daytona, we recognize the value each team member brings and offer benefits designed to support both your professional and personal life:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>We're Investing in You:</strong> Commitment to your professional growth through continuous learning opportunities, advancement potential, and a culture that values your unique contributions.</li>
      <li><strong>Remote Flexibility:</strong> Embrace the ability to work from where you are most productive. Whether from home, a café, or a beach, our remote work options can adapt to your lifestyle.</li>
      <li><strong>Flexible PTO:</strong> Take the time you need, when you need it. Our flexible paid time off policy encourages you to rest, recharge, and maintain a balanced life.</li>
      <li><strong>Paid Parental Leave:</strong> Supporting new parents is important to us. Our comprehensive parental leave policy ensures you can focus on your family when it's most important.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

